---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Card from "../../components/Card/index.astro";
import { SITE } from "../../site-config";
---

<Layout 
  title={`Visual Automation | ${SITE.author.fullName}`} 
  description="Case study for a secure, vision-based workflow automation engine."
>
  <main class="text-white m-auto p-4 md:p-8 max-w-4xl mt-10">
    <a href="/" class="text-primary hover:underline mb-8 inline-block transition-colors">← Back to Grid</a>
    
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Visual Automation Engine</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-neutral-400 mb-10">Computer-vision powered macros for legacy systems and complex UI environments.</p>
    
    <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 mb-4">
       <Card title="The Problem" colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-1">
         <p class="text-sm text-neutral-300 mt-2">
           Many businesses rely on secure or legacy applications that do not offer API access. Automating tasks in these environments typically requires manual, repetitive human input, which is slow and error-prone.
         </p>
       </Card>
       <Card title="The Solution" colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-1">
         <p class="text-sm text-neutral-300 mt-2">
           A robust, Linux-native Python engine that uses screen-reading capabilities and pixel detection to "see" the interface. It reacts instantly to visual changes and executes human-like navigation sequences, bypassing the need for APIs.
         </p>
       </Card>
    </div>

    <Card title="The Tech Stack" colSpan="md:col-span-2" rowSpan="md:row-span-1">
      <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-4">
        <li class="bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-mono">Python 3</li>
        <li class="bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-mono">OpenCV / PIL</li>
        <li class="bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-mono">PyAutoGUI</li>
        <li class="bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-mono">Linux Shell</li>
      </ul>
    </Card>

    <div class="mt-8 rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-neutral-800 bg-[#0c0c0c] font-mono text-sm shadow-2xl">
      <div class="flex items-center px-4 py-3 bg-neutral-900 border-b border-neutral-800">
        <div class="flex space-x-2">
          <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500/80"></div>
          <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/80"></div>
          <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500/80"></div>
        </div>
        <p class="ml-4 text-xs text-neutral-500 flex-1 text-center mr-10">ezradante@EzraDante: ~/projects/vision-macro</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="p-4 md:p-6 text-green-400 min-h-[250px]">
        <p class="text-neutral-300">ezradante@EzraDante:~/projects/vision-macro$ <span class="text-white">./start_engine.sh</span></p>
        
        <div class="mt-3 space-y-2">
          <p class="line opacity-0">[SYSTEM] Booting secure automation environment...</p>
          <p class="line opacity-0">[VISION] Calibrating screen capture region (X:400, Y:300, W:1200, H:800)</p>
          <p class="line opacity-0">[VISION] Awaiting UI state change...</p>
          
          <div class="line opacity-0 text-white border-l-2 border-blue-500 pl-3 my-3 py-2 bg-blue-500/10">
            <p class="font-bold text-blue-300 mb-1">TARGET DETECTED:</p>
            <p>Object Profile: [Submit_Button_v2]</p>
            <p>Confidence Score: <span class="text-green-400">0.98 (HIGH MATCH)</span></p>
          </div>
          
          <p class="line opacity-0">[ACTION] Calculating humanized trajectory curve...</p>
          <p class="line opacity-0">[ACTION] Executing secure click event. <span class="text-blue-400">SUCCESS</span></p>
          <p class="line opacity-0">[SYS_LOG] Action recorded. Resetting vision loop...</p>
          <p class="line opacity-0 flex items-center">[VISION] Monitoring display output... <span class="animate-pulse w-2 h-4 bg-green-400 ml-1 inline-block"></span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <script>
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
      const loader = document.querySelector('.loader');
      if (loader) loader.remove();
    });
  </script>
</Layout>

<style>
  .line {
    animation: appear 0.1s forwards;
  }
  
  .line:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
  .line:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 1.2s; }
  .line:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 1.8s; }
  .line:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 3.5s; } /* Simulates waiting for the screen to change */
  .line:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 3.9s; }
  .line:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 4.2s; }
  .line:nth-child(7) { animation-delay: 4.8s; }
  .line:nth-child(8) { animation-delay: 5.2s; }

  @keyframes appear {
    to {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }
</style>
